-- Google Said in Talks to Buy Groupon, All Things Digital Says
-- B y   S t e v e n   F r o m m
-- 2010-11-19T13:46:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-19/google-is-in-discussions-to-purchase-groupon-all-things-digital-reports.html
Google Inc. is in talks with Groupon
Inc. about buying the company, All Things Digital reported on
its website, citing unidentified "multiple sources close to the
situation."  The price under discussion is "well above" $2 billion to $3
billion that Yahoo! Inc. offered Groupon earlier this year, All
Things Digital reported. Google and Groupon declined comment,
All Things Digital reported.  Groupon has neared a $3 billion valuation, Bloomberg News
reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steven Fromm at 
 sfromm@bloomberg.net  